        "timestamp": "2018-01-29 20:35:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+2\n\nI'm ok with it. We will probably have to do some work regarding certificates. If you want to open a JIRA Jorge that would be good.",
        "patchset_number": 2
